{"tid":1865610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我國將自本（109）年2月7日起，針對14日內曾經入境或居住於中國大陸、香港、澳門的外籍人士，暫緩入境","createTime":"2020-02-06T09:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T10:36:25.000Z","uid":73092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c33da3ba4d4cd486d0c4fd8935f096f6d554d9","tid":1865610,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"2020/02/06<br />\n第039號新聞稿<br />\n<br />\n一、由於我國政府已於本年2月5日將中國大陸全境（含香港、澳門）列為重疫區「二級以上流行地區」，外籍人士只要14日內曾經入境或居住於中國大陸、香港或澳門，暫緩入境我國。即使有特殊原因，我駐外館處也不再受理簽證申請。<br />\n<br />\n二、已持有我國有效居留證而擬返臺的外籍人士，若在14日內曾經入境或居住於中國大陸、香港或澳門者，返臺之後將限制居住，並進行14日的「居家檢疫」措施。<br />\n<br />\n三、上述管制措施將於本年2月7日起正式實施，並持續視疫情狀況調整。（E）"},{"pid":"91b14d19e814582497708ec10d96af16ac0ee29c","tid":1865610,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mofa.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=8742DCE7A2A28761&amp;s=A3BAA07AD9008D3F&amp;fbclid=IwAR2OgV2EybqI34Qt5Z59_GsSTakBcndALTp4NdE0qfu3GGyZO7gbggN81EU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mofa.gov.tw%2FNews_Content.aspx%3Fn%3D8742DCE7A2A28761%26s%3DA3BAA07AD9008D3F%26fbclid%3DIwAR2OgV2EybqI34Qt5Z59_GsSTakBcndALTp4NdE0qfu3GGyZO7gbggN81EU&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=25db8848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mofa.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=8742DCE7A2A28761&amp;s=A3BAA07AD9008D3F&amp;fbclid=IwAR2OgV2EybqI34Qt5Z59_GsSTakBcndALTp4NdE0qfu3GGyZO7gbggN81EU</a>"},{"pid":"8b9198cbf0f57deba6da69e22ef11079863ef049","tid":1865610,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:22:12.000Z","msg":"唔關港澳居民事<br />\n港澳居民而家係有簽證嘅就家居隔離14日，<br />\n冇簽證就申請唔到，去都冇得去"},{"pid":"3ae376d687aaf818035ce619191872053e1dc69a","tid":1865610,"uid":52311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"中華民國 香港唔當外籍"}]}